cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.SI, cs.DS, cs.CE 

The paper deals with network tomography, which is a topic related to computer networks and communication systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also introduces compressed sensing technique, which is a signal processing technique used to efficiently acquire and reconstruct signals. Therefore, cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.SI (Signal Processing) are also likely categories. The paper proposes an algorithm for constructing reflective paths, which involves graph theory and optimization techniques. Therefore, cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) are also possible categories.
